    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        - Adult patients undergoing elective off-pump coronary arterial bypass grafting

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Preoperative LV EF &lt;= 35%

          -  Moderate or severe valvular heart disease

          -  Cardiac arrhythmia

          -  Intracardiac shunt

          -  Severe renal or liver disease

          -  Moderate to severe pulmonary hypertension (mean PAP &gt; 35 mmHg)

          -  Patients with bullous lung disease or combined pneumothorax
      </textblock>
